    "created_at": "2017-04-27T09:35:38Z",
    "updated_at": "2017-04-27T09:35:38Z",
    "body": "We've also observed the same behavior with initial load times of over a second on Windows 10. We spotted it using the `uuid` module (see https://github.com/kelektiv/node-uuid/issues/189#issuecomment-297663423)\r\n\r\nWe've [worked around it](https://gist.github.com/niik/d9a0991a8256cf92225c52e7a2800ad8) for now by using window.crypto as our source of entropy for `uuid` but since we could end up having one of our other dependencies source through the NodeJS crypto module it'd be real nice if we could solve this in electron proper."
  },
